Notice:
	temp and cache dir should be in the same partition so that files can be moved fast.

Dependency:
	gearman
	memcache
	mplayer
	mencoder (component of mplayer)
	ffmpeg
	yamdi (Windows version in distfile/)
	ImageMagick
	7-zip
	flowplayer
	LibreOffice or OpenOffice.org
	unoconv (can be run by python bundled in OOo)
	ghostscript
	firefox 2+
	Pearl Crescent Page Saver (Basic)

Troubleshooting: (FreeBSD)
	unoconv:
		ldconfig -m /usr/local/lib/libreoffice/ure/lib/
		sys.path.append('/usr/local/lib/libreoffice/basis3.3/program')
		os.putenv('URE_BOOTSTRAP','vnd.sun.star.pathname:/usr/local/lib/libreoffice/basis3.3/program/fundamentalbasisrc')

Notes:
	rc.local:
		killall gearman
		killall soffice.bin
		libreoffice -headless -norestore -accept="socket,host=localhost,port=2002;urp;" &
		/usr/local/bin/gearman -w -f webnautilus -- /usr/local/bin/php /home/www/picture/bg_thumb.php &
